WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:01.840
As the saying goes

2
00:00:01.840 --> 00:00:03.060
As expected of a scholar

3
00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:04.380
I want you to take care of it.

4
00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:07.840
By the way, why did you close the door?

5
00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:09.720
Can he still escape?

6
00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:11.520
It's too fake not to lock it.

7
00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:12.620
It's easy to revolt.

8
00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:15.960
Besides, you underestimate a person's survival instinct

9
00:00:15.960 --> 00:00:16.720
Can't bet

10
00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:19.740
In less than 30 West, this Zuo Yuner will escape

11
