12
00:00:22.360 --> 00:00:24.260
I'll twist my head and use it as a urinal for you

13
00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:27.580
Ah, come on out.

14
00:00:29.720 --> 00:00:34.800
I rely on rumors that the eldest lady of my Hou family does not touch the spring water on her index finger

15
00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:36.300
How did he manage it?

16
00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:38.840
If someone chases you with a knife

17
00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:40.580
Trust me, you can outrun a horse

18
00:00:40.600 --> 00:00:41.780
You don't have to.

19
00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:48.900
Now Zuo Yun'er has run away, and then what?

20
00:00:49.400 --> 00:00:50.820
Don't worry, keep watching

21
00:00:51.080 --> 00:00:53.540
Ahhh

22
00:00:54.040 --> 00:00:55.820
I am the daughter of the Zuo Wuhou family

23
00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:57.440
I've been kidnapped.

24
00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:58.560
Please help me

25
00:00:58.560 --> 00:00:59.280
Who kidnapped you?

26
00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:03.300
What are the sons and grandsons who don't get used to each other?

